Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)}被捨棄的 面具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像在做噩夢 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎 昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…我說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜…娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥什麼也沒說 什麼也沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉所期望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉所選擇的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在那裡 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉的人身安全有保障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有布里塔尼亞正規軍 還有朱雀在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然作為敵人他們無比棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但棘手也正體現了這保障的可信度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 就像我曾經期望過的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有我保護 也已…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 聽說這個寺廟是一千年前建的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別提這個了 你看到水槍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明準備了大家的份的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網子 蠟燭 假髮 煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有鈴鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我們是去修學旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上 我是第二次了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太期待修學旅行 興奮得沒睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…其實就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯真像個小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11區新總督即將發表就任致辭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請全體同學到禮堂集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是布里塔尼亞第87皇位繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉·V·布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替日前殉職的卡拉雷斯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出任本屆11區總督
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雙目失明且腿腳不便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總督？那樣的小女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請各位多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說多多關照…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得我都亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然匆忙 有一事希望大家能協助於我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算重建日本行政特區
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟說出這種犯忌的話來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本特區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞人和屬區人民將受到平等對待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11區人可以重獲日本人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛才說日本人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想欺騙我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木朱雀也在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他也一樣是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是殺戮公主的騎士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出賣ZERO的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然過去在日本特區曾發生過不幸的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我認為其目標並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平等 溫柔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色騎士團的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請務必加入日本特區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承認彼此的錯誤 一定可以重來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅信這點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會說出重建日本特區…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 尤菲皇姐想做的事是正確的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 錯的不是尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換乘急行列車的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在下車後到站台對面的3號線等待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站可換乘千京線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(0,700)}各站停車將在5號站台…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}已經不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是ZERO 還是我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個總督也和殺戮公主尤菲米婭一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 日本人誰也不會參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用甜言蜜語把人引出來 然後趕盡殺絕？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少瞧不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 今後怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是跟布里塔尼亞決戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的Knightmare可只剩下紅蓮一架了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 只要ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂耶殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城先生說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎麼不見ZERO大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新婚妻子特地趕來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在中華聯邦時他也連封信都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是出軌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 他是騙人的 神樂耶殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂英雄愛美人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑒於成年男子的生理狀況…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了 你比看起來更成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的時候 感謝你陪伴他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不足掛齒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 卡蓮小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支持ZERO大人的三位…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是三宮女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}註：三宮女是女兒節用來裝飾的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮女？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要追尋黑色騎士團 出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精密檢查還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點還是老樣子 他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了完成Conquista…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑麥麵包加黃姜 日本砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混合後再加芥末醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至今為止所作所為 都是為了娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是布里塔尼亞第87皇位繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉·V·布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替日前殉職的卡拉雷斯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉或許已察覺了我的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使如此 她還是說要繼承尤菲的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是為了這 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了先給錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 窮光蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你們不也一樣是11區人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要這個 就拿錢來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人吃日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是以布里塔尼亞人走狗的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說日本人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要布里塔尼亞人同情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是11區人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區學生少管人家做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是自願為我所用的 學生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我 賤民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我做俯臥撐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科爾恰克先生 您做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下蹲運動 嗥叫 拍手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回這兒來也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 他活著更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…光是不當ZERO那很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不是多浪漫的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣下去 黑色騎士團就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「為娜娜莉而存在的ZERO」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修這麼說呢 瑪莉安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道 他到底想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然來了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是ZERO…你開始的地方
Comment: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修 我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以靠這個回到懷念的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:11:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是失敗了一次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再想作戰計劃挽回不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像往常一樣下命令給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開Knightmare？還是誘餌搜查？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼我都聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安慰我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用女人才能做到的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給了我們夢想 就要負責任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把我們騙到底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要把完美的ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演到底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務是監視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是痛苦的重負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO是 黑色騎士團是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 娜娜莉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11區就能獲得和平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也恢復到普通學生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福生活就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求幸福 有什麼不對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會傷害到任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還可以將一切歸零
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 只有我不會去任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠和哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何志願提出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出任ZERO復活後的11區總督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前一直受到哥哥的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在雖然他行蹤不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他一定還在關注著我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要做出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會給哥哥丟臉的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重哦 那面具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要肩負整個世界的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是必須有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是布里塔尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴艦所屬及航路 與申報有異
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請停船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在將進行強行臨檢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將等待十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前所有乘員解除武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到甲板上站好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 大家都去修學旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 空無一人的鳥籠正適合現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修也來放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭用剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？修學旅行呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是就我們去了 你會哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵不在於去哪裡 而是跟誰一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說能實現願望 就做了試試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:16:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過怎麼也想不起是跟誰學的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你許了什麼願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經實現了 一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和大家一起放煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有魯路修和羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只折了一隻 所以只實現了魯魯這份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得以前曾跟娜娜莉 朱雀說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若幸福有形態的話 那會是怎樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了 就像朱雀說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許幸福就像玻璃一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為平時從未察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它確實存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據就是 稍微改變看的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃就會映照出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:17:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何東西更雄辯地主張自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說折一千隻這種紙鶴 就能實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉想許什麼願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一個溫柔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的世界就近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使為虛偽的記憶所玷污
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻更顯出透明的琉璃色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我們的友情所感動了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有可愛的一面嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再來這裡一起放煙花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定 一定要再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不僅是為了娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 爆破油輪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使敵方聲納失效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下俯配平30度 急速潛航
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的聯絡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然斷絕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該又打算潛入海底逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動PortmanII
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以被動模式確認
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從動力音判斷應該是水中型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降低深度 被發現就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASROC（反潛導彈）發射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要驚慌 這是無的放矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以θ地點為中心張開包圍網
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能把敵人逼出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦內各部進水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一移動會被對方捕捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Q1 聽到嗎 Q1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下俯配平50度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向地點L14急速潛航
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 太遲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續投放深水炸彈 保持包圍網
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向正面 魚雷全彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用定時信管設40秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有敵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了相信他 還有別的辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設定信管後 全彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認魚雷發射音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到敵方位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人在地點L14
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中攻擊 等它浮上我來捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnmingliu\fs16\pos(320,442)\b}火蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnmingliu\fs16\pos(565,442)}藍海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salamander呼叫BlueDolphin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向定點改變發射角度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Portman佈陣區域 傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網眼不大 別設錯目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Salamander 已確認
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標設定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈投射管 旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固定錨後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各員 準備承受衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 甲烷水合物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木卿 水泡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水泡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉舵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 即將翻船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底湧起巨大的水泡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 這不是叫援軍就能解決的問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合倖存的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將黑色騎士團…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO往這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的回答嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍就是違抗君令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定接受娜娜莉總督的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是日本特區的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是投降了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.05,0:21:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO下令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色騎士團全員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入日本特區！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你確實正面帶笑容 正在享受
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 那並非真實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏在你那笑容背後的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:23:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若只有一人知道真相 擁有救贖的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.01,0:23:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那麼我理當反抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:23:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名為和平的統治
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔑視 欺瞞我們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們視作玩物的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以ZERO的名義…


